{"tid":437912,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"［求救］台證問題","createTime":"2017-10-16T12:13:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-18T03:16:48.000Z","uid":124824,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0395d7964295d1627d633e970d9e93b4a2150482","tid":437912,"uid":124824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T12:13:11.000Z","msg":"各位爸絲打，求求各位嘅幫忙<br />\n我屋企人今晚就飛 但係台證上出現咗問題<br />\n我有位屋企人原來非港澳出生 <br />\n如果依加上網搞台證係咪唔會批？<br />\n其實依加係咪等於唔洗去 <br />\n唔洗去我叫佢地翻屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n唔該曬各位巴絲打 求協助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a59d0c880031d89fe4ecf880704a96efa9a8776a","tid":437912,"uid":124824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T12:15:07.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a4b27f84f158ddf8239d70e432cb33f953a0e01","tid":437912,"uid":39608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T12:21:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/361185/page/1?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/361185/page/1?ref=android</a>"},{"pid":"ce27cf1cf32a65cb7a69eb86a0082b120d4ba3aa","tid":437912,"uid":124824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T12:21:38.000Z","msg":"問咗職員就話<br />\n上網唔得 一定要去金鐘搞...<br />\n咁係咪此po已完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0195acb192117e60ece2dc8865ecd00c986c7ea9","tid":437912,"uid":36511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T12:24:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>各位爸絲打，求求各位嘅幫忙<br />\n我屋企人今晚就飛 但係台證上出現咗問題<br />\n我有位屋企人原來非港澳出生 <br />\n如果依加上網搞台證係咪唔會批？<br />\n其實依加係咪等於唔洗去 <br />\n唔洗去我叫佢地翻屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n唔該曬各位巴絲打 求協助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢有無特區護照，有嘅應該可以照申請同用特區護照過境，但會唔會咁快批到我就唔知，如果唔係好似可以落地簽。<br />\n<br />\n但如果佢用過另一本護照入台灣，就要用另一本護照先可以入台灣，唔洗台證。<br />\n<br />\n利申，九月中過一次伏，同行友人之前用過英國護照過境，點知佢上次淨係帶左特區護照同台證，無得入境"},{"pid":"4d1b2c27c42f57eaf7fe4a95b754565a9e12773d","tid":437912,"uid":124824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T12:24:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/361185/page/1?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/361185/page/1?ref=android</a></blockquote><br />\n爸打唔該曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5de0e5e8cde29ca71554e3b1bcb4a17e5f09c95d","tid":437912,"uid":124824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T12:27:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢有無特區護照，有嘅應該可以照申請同用特區護照過境，但會唔會咁快批到我就唔知，如果唔係好似可以落地簽。<br />\n<br />\n但如果佢用過另一本護照入台灣，就要用另一本護照先可以入台灣，唔洗台證。<br />\n<br />\n利申，九月中過一次伏，同行友人之前用過英國護照過境，點知佢上次淨係帶左特區護照同台證，無得入境</blockquote><br />\n謝謝巴打<br />\n特區個到出生地點 唔係香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b3f74bb2b6f0457ae44e746b46f86d985405f19","tid":437912,"uid":128101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T15:17:30.000Z","msg":"最後點呀？"},{"pid":"4e8101003a40a6c004803af74e54de0f2aba2574","tid":437912,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T17:46:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/300020/page/1?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/300020/page/1?ref=android</a>"},{"pid":"62a9e045187d6bb7a5bd2da1145849c8209a7758","tid":437912,"uid":143580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T03:16:48.000Z","msg":"如果有港澳護照但非呢兩地岀生，都可以上網整。但就唔會即刻有。上網交完係辦公時間內有人睇過無問題會send email通知你翻去log in交錢咁，最快都要兩三日。唔知你家人咩情況啦最後，但俾定資料你先。<br />\n<a href=\"https://coa.immigration.gov.tw/coa-frontend/overseas-honk-macao\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcoa.immigration.gov.tw%2Fcoa-frontend%2Foverseas-honk-macao&d=iHe0AXGv8ycdxYU%2FahLYx%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=7463a187\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://coa.immigration.gov.tw/coa-frontend/overseas-honk-macao</a>"}]}